Another One Bites The Dust
Words and music by John Deacon
Transcribed by Philipp (PraxisNothaft@t-online.de) 
About the sounds and other Info's:
  Guitar 1:Fat tube-distortion,plays fills
  Guitar 2:The same as guitar 1
  Guitar 3:clean funk sound,rythm guitar
  Guitar 4:With a little bit of overdrive,a very dry sound,plays the same as
           the bass line and is palm muted throughout!
  "." means "staccato"
  x=muffled strings

On the record,all guitars are tuned one semitone up to F,live it's played like 
here in Em

Often used riff(Git.4)
1 + 2 + 3 + 4 +  1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + 
