BASS:



Artist:Queen
Title:Another one bites the dust
Tuning:EADG
Tabber:Justin van Uum

Main riff,there are 3 variations of it.
G-------------------------|
D-------------------------|
A-1--------------------1--|this one is used more than the second one,but not
E---4-1-1-1--1-1-1-4-1----|that much as the third variation.

G-----------------------|
D-----------------------|
A--------------------1--|this one is played after the chorus and bridge.
E-4-1-1-1--1-1-1-4-1----|

G--------------------|
D--------------------|
A------------------1-| this is used the most
E-1-1-1--1-1-1-4-1---|

Chorus
G--------------------------------------------------------|
D------------6----------------------------6--------------|
A-4-4--4-5-6--4--4-4--4-5-6----4-4--4-5-6--4-------------|
E---------------------------6-----------------6-6--6-7-8-|

Bridge
G-----------------|
D-----------------|
A-----------------|
E-3---9-7-7-7-7-3-|

That's it then.Enjoy!